{"tid":1655380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★No $37.5？】港經濟前景嚴峻　最低工資或下調","createTime":"2019-10-15T04:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T07:34:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"9cd4bd74a338d5c2d401f183c862d47dfd1dead2","tid":1655380,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:42:17.000Z","msg":"反修例衝突令旅遊及零售業生意減，行內僱員停薪放假，今年建築業工人亦凍薪，最低工資委員會主席王沛詩表示，反修例風波對香港經濟的影響嚴峻，最低工資水平「並無規定一定上、落或打橫」，意味未來最低工資水平有上調、下調或凍結的可能。<br />\n今年5月1日最低工資由34.5港元升至37.5港元，升幅8.7%，最低工資委員會將於明年底檢討最低工資水平的建議。王稱委員會擔心近4個月的示威活動及中美貿易戰等不明朗因素，會密切關注經濟狀況，檢討及制訂最低工資水平會參考一系列經濟指標，包括整體經濟狀況、勞工市場、競爭力及社會共融等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191015/bkn-20191015120839746-1015_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191015%2Fbkn-20191015120839746-1015_00822_001.html&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=d2a2aa0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191015/bkn-20191015120839746-1015_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"dd924ff91144cdd78a5f342320ca4a599c319b37","tid":1655380,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:42:41.000Z","msg":"Free<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b16e726a23c85e3535c3b64792eaa13cf5dcda0","tid":1655380,"uid":126283,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:43:36.000Z","msg":"又多班人connect埋同政府死撚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fd5c432613fd9c2e2478c66d5085d421279489","tid":1655380,"uid":56260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"weco